SpeechRecogn --- Translate your speech into text, Using Google's Speech Recognition API


----------------------------------
File Structure

	speech_sample.pl	-	From Mike Pultz. Can be use as a reference of Google's API
	upload_audio.py		-	Currently experimental. Need to install requests module.

----------------------------------
Usage

	speech_sample.pl YourAudioRecord.flac
	upload_audio.py YourAudioRecord.flac